  name: "Hair-Trigger Reflexes"
  label: null
  type: null
  description: "At 2nd level, as long as she has at least 1 grit point, a thronewarden\
    \ can act in a surprise round even if she doesn't notice her enemies, though she\
    \ remains flat-footed until she acts. In addition, she gains a +1 bonus on initiative\
    \ checks. This bonus increases by 1 for every 4 gunslinger levels beyond 2nd.\
    \ Finally, at 10th level, she can spend 1 grit point to take both a standard action\
    \ and a move action (or a full-round action) during the surprise round."
  effects: null
  prerequisites: null
  source: "Pathfinder Player Companion: Heroes of the High Court"
